analysis.significance: Shows Epstein sharing politically charged content about election interference allegations during the 2016 presidential campaign

analysis.summary: Jeffrey Epstein emails his attorney Darren Indyke a YouTube video titled 'Rigging the Election' that alleges the Clinton campaign and DNC incited violence at Trump rallies, marked with high importance during the 2016 presidential election.
